name: Experiment Or Die #1
description: I've been fascinated by the dichotomy between our real lives and the life and worlds depicted in movies, television, books and video games. In this ongoing series of collages I will create 1 a day for a year using images I've shot over the last 20 years, found objects, textures and references from the pop culture that has helped mold me as an artist. Each design will be an edition of 2, no more, no less. ig:Nikejerk
